# Keep the superseded site off the public deploy. _archive/ holds the previous
# pages, which contain invented pricing, promotions that do not exist and
# seventeen fabricated staff biographies. They are kept for reference only and
# must never be reachable at a URL.
/_archive

# Internal production documentation, not website content.
/DESIGN.md

# Build tooling and its inputs. The site serves assets/img/ derivatives only;
# the root-level originals are build sources and are not referenced at runtime.
/tools
/*.jpg
/*.webp
/*.zip
